@div proverb 24.2

24.2.2. šah₂# [niga] ab#-šum-de₃ niŋ₂!# [i₃-gu₇-a-ŋu₁₀ ga-ab-sug₆-e-še]
#lem: šah[pig]; niga[fattened]; šum[slaughter]; niŋ[thing]; gu[eat]; sug[replace]
#etcsl: line-id=24.2.2

#note: cf. 6.1.09.a12-13, 6.1.19.b1-2, 6.1.21.b4-5, 6.2.5: YBC 4677 ll. 1-4

24.2.3. šah₂-ze₂#-eh-tur-e šu# [al-gu₄-ud-gu₄-ud-de₃] sag₉-ga-aš-am₃ ŋe₂₆-e# [nu-gu₇-e-še]
#lem: šahzehtur[piglet]; šu[hand]; gud[jump (on)]; sag[good]; ŋaʾe[I]; gu[eat]
#etcsl: line-id=24.2.3

@end proverb

